agonal incisions in flesh. Using a pastry brush, brush za'atar oil mixture over aubergines. Roast for 20-25 minutes (180°C) until soft and browned on edges. Meanwhile, cook bulgar wheat."},{"content":"Place water in mixing bowl then insert simmering basket. Weigh in bulgar wheat and cook <b>15 min\/100°C\/speed 4<b>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula then stir bulgar wheat with a fork."},{"content":"Place spinach on a large serving platter. Season cooked bulgar wheat with salt and pepper, scatter over spinach, then top with roasted aubergine slices."},{"content":"Add chickpeas, cherry tomatoes, olives and red onion. Top with feta and pomegranate, then drizzle with green tahini dressing. Serve immediately."}],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","6 portions"]}